ROURKE PLEADS NOT GUILTY TO SPOUSAL ABUSE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Actor Mickey Rourke pleaded not guilty Thursday to a charge that he beat his 
estranged wife, his "Wild Orchid" co-star Carre Otis, at a Hollywood office. 
</P>
<P>
 Rourke, who lives in Miami, did not appear for the Los Angeles Municipal Court 
