discussion and are supportive of Rogers' brand of hardheaded conservatism are 
necessarily racist. However proud we may be of our heritage, many, many of us 
love and honor those of African descent whose ancestors, as much or more than 
our own, helped to build this country with pick and shovel and hoe.  
</P>
<P>
 Liberals don't have a monopoly on noble feelings -- just on foolishness and 
insincerity. 
</P>
<P>
