15.2 Anaheim (proposed) 15.0 Houston 15.0 Chicago 14.9 Cleveland 14.5 Los 
Angeles 14.0 St. Louis 13.9 New York 13.3* Knoxville 13.3 Memphis 13.3 Atlanta 
