<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 9, 1994, Friday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 2; Metro Desk 
