<P>
SANTA ANA VALLEY HIRES AQUATICS DIRECTOR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Sandra Schneider has been hired to direct the aquatics program at Santa Ana 
Valley, Athletic Director Leon Smith said Thursday. 
</P>
<P>
 Schneider, a former goalkeeper for the U.S. women's water polo team, will 
coach water polo and swimming. 
</P>
