<P>
 "People don't seem to care about each other very much anymore. People don't 
talk to strangers on the streets and people are paranoid with each other. There 
doesn't seem to be a general community feeling of happiness." 
</P>
<P>
 Sara Parks, 17, senior, Laguna Hills 
</P>
