<TEXT>
<P>
 Pacific Chorale music director John Alexander has been appointed director of 
choral activities and conductor of the University Singers and Men's Chorus at 
Cal State Fullerton, effective immediately. He will continue to direct the 
Pacific Chorale. The choral season opens at the university on Dec. 2 with a 
concert in the Campus Little Theater. 
</P>
<P>
 Compiled by Ken Williams 
</P>
