<P>
 Group Seeks Ban on Leg Cramp Drug: Public Citizen's Health Research Group 
asked the Food and Drug Administration to immediately ban quinine sulfate, a 
prescription drug for nighttime leg cramps, citing reports that it is dangerous 
as well as ineffective.The drug is sold in prescription and over-the-counter 
