<P>
PAINE GETS SHUTTLE BY UNITED CONTRACT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 United Airlines has chosen Paine & Associates to handle public relations for 
the launch of its new service, Shuttle by United. 
</P>
<P>
 Shuttle by United is set to offer low fares and frequent daily departures for 
short trips between West Coast cities.Service between San Francisco, Los 
Angeles, Oakland, Las Vegas, Seattle, Ontario, Burbank, San Diego and 
Sacramento is scheduled to start on Oct. 1, and will begin with 184 daily 
departures. By year's end, Shuttle by United expects to expand its operations 
to five additional West Coast cities and will add to the number of scheduled 
departures. 
</P>
<P>
 Terms of the deal were not released, but competitors estimated Paine & 
Associates would earn less than $200,000 on the public relations contract. 
</P>
<P>
 Paine & Associates, established in 1986, is Orange County's largest public 
relations firm. 
