<P>
 Orange Coast Title Co.: The company said Thursday it has purchased Courtesy 
Title of Salt Lake City, Utah.The terms of the transaction were not disclosed. 
</P>
<P>
 Courtesy was founded just a year ago, but the brisk business it has done 
during Utah's real estate boom made it an attractive purchase for Orange Coast, 
